Since 2011, Global Citizen has registered more than 19 million “actions” from supporters, targeting a wide range of different goals.
According to Global Citizen, these actions have helped world leaders commit to making policy proposals worth more than $37 billion that will change the lives of 2.25 billion people by 2030.
